<template><div><p>The Python language has many similarities to Perl, C, and Java. However, there are some definite differences between the languages.</p>
<h2 id="first-python-program" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#first-python-program"><span>First Python Program</span></a></h2>
